{"tid":229009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心「石湖风」！大雨压境 强阵风先来袭","createTime":"2017-05-04T10:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T10:24:10.000Z","uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1c28118ea6256b6b1c56d442c2d4255eaed6c5","tid":229009,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:22:33.000Z","msg":"与低压槽相关的一道雷雨带，正由西北向东南移动，横过珠江口一带。天文台分别在上8时50分和9时11分，发出特别天气提示，指预料有高达时速70公里或以上的阵风（石湖风）吹袭香港；香港广泛地区短期内可能受大雨影响，市民应提高警觉。<br />\n<br />\n天文台在春夏季不时发天气提示，警告有强阵风来袭，民间俗称「打石湖」或「石湖风」，学术称为「下击暴流」（Downburst）。<br />\n石湖风来袭前，雷达图上通常看到一条狭长的强烈雷雨带，有时呈弧形弯弓状，破坏力不容忽视，因其横扫之处，风速会瞬间飙升，风向突转，阵风可高达时速百多公里，有时更夹杂冰雹及龙卷风。<br />\n华南沿岸的石湖风在春夏之交较常见，通常由冷锋或低压槽的强烈雷雨带引起。春末夏初的石湖风，通常由西北方吹来，故又称「西北石湖风」，今次便是一例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170504/small/1493863445_8580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Fsmall%2F1493863445_8580.png&h=cf42683a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台早上9时雷达图。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170504/small/1493880944_9c61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Fsmall%2F1493880944_9c61.jpg&h=8a47750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱永伦摄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170504/small/1493880980_5f74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Fsmall%2F1493880980_5f74.jpg&h=d3a3cd15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱永伦摄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170504/small/1493880970_78c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Fsmall%2F1493880970_78c3.jpg&h=5ffd6fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱永伦摄"},{"pid":"952d85ffc878a801a63eed0fc6ae9802e0512945","tid":2290